<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-21 14:13 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0599 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u v BC-HEARST-NEWS-BUDGET-HN     06-21 0368
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-HEARST-NEWS-BUDGET-HNS </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; Wednesday, June 21, 2000 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR;  &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
