a lot of guts to be out. (Ringel, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).18
</P>
<P>
   AUDIO-KDLANG _ Lede CD review: New KD Lang album is a groovy
pastiche of late '60s summer pop, echoing the Turtles and the Mamas
and the Papas. (BLongino, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 9.
