   DEATH-PERRY _ AUSTIN, Texas _ Lt. Gov. Rick Perry and Attorney
General John Cornyn step into the fray, proclaiming Gary Graham's
guilt and saying the state's justice system is sound and fair.
(Heath, Austin American-Statesman). 10-12. MOVED.
