behind his testimony that the nephew of Ethel Kennedy told him more
than 20 years ago that he had murdered a young girl. By Brian
MacQuarrie. 900 words.
</P>
<P>
   SCI-BRAINS (Undated) _ Researchers say they have activated a
latent self-repair system in the brains of animals, getting new
neurons to grow in brain regions where they don't normally grow. By
Richard Saltus. 900 words.
</P>
