<P>
   CALIF-ECONOMY (Los Angeles) _ California's robust economy is
expected to continue to expand in the coming years, albeit at a
more moderate rate than currently, a University of California, Los
Angeles, survey released Wednesday predicts. By Chris Sieroty.
</P>
<P>
   X X X
