National Association of Hispanic Journalists tonight after
campaigning for Hispanic votes in Southern California earlier in
the day. By JOHN GONZALEZ.
</P>
<P>
   GORE-SOCIAL-SECURITY (Undated) _ Vice President Al Gore
continues to tout his plan to save Social Security while creating a
new retirement option for Americans as he campaigns in the Midwest.
By PATTY REINERT.
</P>
