<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-21 22:05 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1098 &Cx1f; taf-z
u p BC-LABOR-POLITICS-NYT &LR;      06-21 0889
